Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:06.85,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:08.58,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我是三班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:09.68,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我二班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:11.14,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:13.25,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我是一班…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.86,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,三個人都分開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:17.86,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,有誰分在一起了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:20.10,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,田徑部的都沒有分在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:21.16,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.84,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,沒事啦 反正社團活動的時候還能見面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:23.83,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:25.78,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,今年會不會有一年生加入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:26.75,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真希望多來些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:28.54,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我忘記做海報了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:29.08,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:30.47,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,比良拜託我做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.70,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是招收部員的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:32.49,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:32.98,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:33.48,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:35.73,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好嘞 我們也要大幹一場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.70,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,全力以赴哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.62,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是吧 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:44.94,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,今天開始 我是初三的學生了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.12,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,同學們 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:25.99,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,四月櫻花盛放 新學期自此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:33.22,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,希望新入學的同學珍惜這份新鮮感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:38.84,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,並希望這份感覺能成為充實你們校園生活的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.86,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,升入二年級和三年級的各位也分配了新的班級…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.50,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,緊張死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:02.01,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,冷靜 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.02,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:21.39,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,即便在中學生之間也存在著差別社會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.26,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,上游和下游
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.52,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,輝煌的社團和一般的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.96,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,外表和成績
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:35.97,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,運用著各自的武器 相互試探上下關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:41.80,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你可真受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:42.85,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真是浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:43.66,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.17,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,受歡迎的傢伙 真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.57,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,快住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.57,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好重好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:52.84,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,聽我說聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.63,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.41,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,這裡不痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:55.91,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,肩膀上來一砣子 來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:56.43,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:56.94,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.20,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:58.83,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.84,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,要不你也來試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.40,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:01.76,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,一點都不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.73,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你們兩個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.79,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.02,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是我哦 心咲 還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.29,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小學三年級的時候我們是一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.48,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,田徑部的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:18.99,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.01,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你認識她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.22,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,涼子來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.51,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好了 都回到座位上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:40.02,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真希望多來些一年生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.15,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.31,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我們也都三年級了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.79,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好 那就全力以赴吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:45.28,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,全力以赴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:46.65,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,等等 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.46,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,寫成犬大大募集了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.26,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,居然寫成犬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:05:59.39,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:05:59.95,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:00.93,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.13,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,要給我看你的小說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.20,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,才不給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.13,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,鑰匙我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.85,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,準備 跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.64,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,茜 擺臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.85,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,水野 你還可以再快點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.25,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.61,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:16.82,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.83,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,今天一起出去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.99,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.55,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你要去洗個澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.53,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.03,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,孩子他爸 快把電視關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.23,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.90,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,肚子好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.63,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,四位 裡面請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.32,Tsuki - Message,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(968.8,1001.6)\frz3.527}{\k50}好 {\k20}加{\k20}油{\k20}吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.44,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,就知道聊Line
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:40.94,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,有什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.22,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是之前的那孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.10,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,水拿來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:48.38,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.00,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小太郎選好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.32,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我要自助飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.27,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,喝茶就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.98,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,多吃一點啊 社團活動那麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.25,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.02,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我要沙拉意麵和自助飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.33,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,就這點？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.45,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}到了家庭餐廳就喝下啤酒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.76,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}媽媽要這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.04,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,奶汁烤菜 還有千層麵都不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.61,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真是的 要不我來給你選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:27.39,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,要不我吃意大利麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.42,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,爸爸真煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.08,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小太郎也要飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.95,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小太郎要自助飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:36.20,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,孩子他媽 幫忙按下鈴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.19,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.65,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小太郎 你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.28,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我要自助飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.85,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,太宰曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:56.26,Tsuki - text - note,,0,0,0,,出自太宰治《斜陽》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:56.26,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,活著 啊 這是一件多麼難以應付 令人無法喘息的偉業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.85,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,茜 要不要點一份炒菠菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.45,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,補點鐵對身體好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.90,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,會不會點太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.51,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,茜你也多吃點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.13,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,馬上要大會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:08.98,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,為了身體得多吃點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.66,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.07,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:15.38,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你好多肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.08,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真是的 我去拿飲料
