Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.90,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,還剩翹毛同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:07.54,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:35.39,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,永原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.00,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,昨天看Line了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.41,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你沒回覆我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.15,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 在電玩中心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.47,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.04,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.15,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.05,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉啦 節子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.50,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,之前也無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.16,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,太鼓我Full Combo了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.73,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,誒？好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.25,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,太鼓是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:51.91,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.89,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,太鼓鐵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:57.06,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,這個超帥的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:58.79,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.11,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,小茜去廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:06.96,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:10.64,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.53,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,下週有祭典的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.22,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:58.30,Tsuki - book,,0,0,0,,{\fs(100)\fn@方正静蕾简体\frz280.4\move(721.6,577.6,846,528,818,5781)}老師連我的内褲上有薔薇花刺繡也不知道。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.41,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,這篇短篇很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:07.28,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,雖然是太宰治以女性的第一人稱獨白來寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:11.10,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,但是女孩子的心思 普通男孩子肯定搞不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:12.73,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.69,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,給 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.17,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,之前說好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.26,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,煮麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:25.35,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是一個叫Happy End的民族搖滾樂隊組合的首張專輯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:29.07,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,樂隊成員之後全部都成為了音樂界的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.41,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,是個超厲害的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.28,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,隨你什麼時候還都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.09,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.43,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:46.50,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,請給我這本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.12,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,附贈這本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.13,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,各種書都看一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.00,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,AZUMI 道具組的集會你沒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.02,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:20.00,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,其他人都在工作 你也要來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:20.78,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.16,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,Line
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.52,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}體育倉庫有一塊得分板 你去拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:25.64,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.84,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.32,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,啊 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.64,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我忘記聯繫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.63,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,有道具組的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:23.56,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,Line
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:25.60,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.33,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,建了一個道具組的群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.09,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,現在沒帶手機…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:40.23,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,那就 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.92,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.38,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.38,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:58.97,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.41,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,多對不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.47,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,但是你的社團活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.56,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,Line跟他們說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.35,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,一起來搬快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.64,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:19.31,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.06,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,背上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.12,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.52,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:34.99,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:37.16,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.08,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
