Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:08.91,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,太宰治說過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:13.77,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,幸福感這種東西會沉到悲哀的河底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:13.77,Tsuki - text - note,,0,0,0,,註：出自太宰治《斜陽》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:17.91,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,隱隱發光 彷彿砂金一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:26.01,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:27.08,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.21,Tsuki - text,,0,0,0,,看我整你
